a]] || [[Washington (state)|Washington]] || [[Cascade Collegiate Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Faulkner University]]\n| Eagles || [[Montgomery, Alabama|Montgomery]] || [[Alabama]] || [[Southern States Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Fisher College]]\n| Falcons || [[Boston]] || [[Massachusetts]] || [[NAIA independent schools|Association of Independent Institutions]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Fisk University]]\n| Bulldogs || [[Nashville, Tennessee|Nashville]] || [[Tennessee]] || [[NAIA independent schools|Association of Independent Institutions]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Florida College]]\n| Falcons || [[Temple Terrace, Florida|Temple Terrace]] || [[Florida]] || [[Southern States Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Florida Memorial University]]\n| [[Florida Memorial University Lions|Lions]] || [[Miami Gardens, Florida|Miami Gardens]] || [[Florida]] || [[Sun Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Florida National University]]\n| Conquistadors || [[Miami, Florida|Miami]] || [[Florida]] || [[Association of Independent Institutions]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aiisports.com/members.php#2733|title=Association of Independent Institutions|website=www.aiisports.com|accessdate=September 7, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Freed\u2013Hardeman University]]\n| Lions || [[Henderson, Tennessee|Henderson]] || [[Tennessee]] || [[American Midwest Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Friends University]]\n| [[Friends Falcons|Falcons]] || [[Wichita, Kansas|Wichita]] || [[Kansas]] || [[Kansas Collegiate Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Georgetown College]]\n| Tigers || [[Georgetown, Kentucky|Georgetown]] || [[Kentucky]] || [[Mid-South Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Georgia Gwinnett College]]*\n| Grizzlies || [[Lawrenceville, Georgia|Lawrenceville]] || [[Georgia (U.S. state)|Georgia]] || [[NAIA independent schools|Association of Independent Institutions]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Goshen College]]\n| Maple Leafs || [[Goshen, Indiana|Goshen]] || [[Indiana]] || [[Crossroads League]]\n|-\n!scope=